---
title: Spiced Pork Loin & Roast Veggie Toss with Garlic Yogurt & Dill
description: It's meat and three veg, but not as you know it. Reinvent this everyday meal by simply tossing the roasted
veggies with baby spinach and topping your golden spiced pork with a dollop of yoghurt. And there you have
it folks, a classic meal that never disappoints.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving*
